' ============================================
' Value chain dependencies
' ============================================

UserNeeds --> WebApplication : Uses
UserNeeds --> MobileApplication : Uses

WebApplication --> MessageService : Depends on
WebApplication --> AuthService : Depends on
WebApplication --> CallService : Depends on
WebApplication --> FileService : Depends on
WebApplication --> SearchService : Depends on

MobileApplication --> MessageService : Depends on
MobileApplication --> AuthService : Depends on
MobileApplication --> CallService : Depends on
MobileApplication --> FileService : Depends on
MobileApplication --> NotificationService : Depends on

MessageService --> DatabaseService : Needs
MessageService --> CacheService : Needs
MessageService --> WebSocketService : Needs

AuthService --> DatabaseService : Needs
AuthService --> CacheService : Needs

CallService --> WebRTCService : Needs
CallService --> DatabaseService : Needs

FileService --> StorageService : Needs
FileService --> CDNService : Needs

SearchService --> SearchEngine : Needs
SearchEngine --> DatabaseService : Needs

NotificationService --> WebSocketService : Needs

StorageService --> CDNService : Uses

ContainerService --> DatabaseService : Hosts
ContainerService --> CacheService : Hosts
ContainerService --> StorageService : Hosts

' ============================================
' Evolution notes
' ============================================

note top of AIAssistant
  **Genesis**
  
  Novel capabilities:
  - AI assistant: recommendations, auto-reply
  - Smart search: semantic, context
  - Advanced WebRTC: low latency, adaptive
  - High differentiation and uncertainty
end note

note top of MessageService
  **Custom Built**
  
  Core platform:
  - Messaging: routing, state, push
  - Call service: WebRTC signalling
  - File service: custom logic, permissions
  - Ongoing investment and tuning
end note

note top of WebApplication
  **Product**
  
  Standard products:
  - Web: Next.js, React
  - Mobile: Flutter
  - Auth: JWT, Passport
  - Push: FCM/APNs
  - Stable delivery
end note

note top of DatabaseService
  **Commodity**
  
  Infrastructure:
  - DB, cache, storage, CDN, containers
  - Standard cloud services
  - Easy to replace or procure
  - Cost optimisation target
end note

